      <title>特朗普坚称自己大幅领先哈里斯，为 2024 年大选存疑铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/trump-claims-he-s-beating-harris-setting-stage-for-2024-election-doubts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和他的盟友告诉支持者，除非出现舞弊行为，否则他们将取得压倒性胜利 - 如果选举结果不利于共和党，这将引发众怒并引发法律挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/trump-claims-he-s-beating-harris-setting-stage-for-2024-election-doubts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿斯利康首席执行官接受调查 其争夺中国市场地位成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/astrazeneca-s-drive-for-china-dominance-in-focus-as-chief-probed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对阿斯利康公司的调查已达到最高层，该公司当地总裁王雷也受牵连，这家中国最成功的西方制药公司的未来也受到质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/astrazeneca-s-drive-for-china-dominance-in-focus-as-chief-probed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 08:10:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙搁置能源暴利税，计划将银行税延长至 2027 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/spain-shelves-energy-windfall-tax-plans-to-extend-bank-levy-to-2027</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙执政的社会党与议会伙伴达成协议，将银行暴利税延长三年。]]></description>
