    <item>
      <title>越南媒体称博客作者因发表反政府内容被判入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/vietnam-gives-blogger-jail-term-for-anti-state-content-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 VietnamPlus 新闻网援引河内人民法院的信息称，博客作者 Duong Van Thai 因传播反党反国家内容被法院判处 12 年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/vietnam-gives-blogger-jail-term-for-anti-state-content-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 06:46:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国前央行行长竞选非政治性董事会主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/former-thai-central-bankers-pitch-for-apolitical-board-chair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，泰国政府正推举前财政部长候选人，以加强对货币当局的控制，一群前泰国央行行长呼吁任命一位非政治人士担任央行行长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/former-thai-central-bankers-pitch-for-apolitical-board-chair</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 05:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究称特朗普关税将导致韩国经济萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/south-korean-economy-would-shrink-under-trump-duties-study-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家政府下属智库表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫并提高对贸易伙伴的关税，韩国经济可能遭遇萎缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/south-korean-economy-would-shrink-under-trump-duties-study-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 04:38:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜发射史上飞行时间最长的洲际弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-further-fueling-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在朝鲜向俄罗斯派兵引发紧张局势之际，朝鲜发射了一枚洲际弹道导弹，其飞行时间比金正恩政权之前试射的任何一枚导弹都要长。随后，美国和韩国举行了联合空中演习，以展示武力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-further-fueling-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 22:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯重振大国，力图“重建”英国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/reeves-resurrects-big-state-in-labour-s-bid-to-rebuild-britain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯承诺，工党十多年来的第一份预算将结束紧缩政策，打破经济停滞的束缚。她提出的计划需要很长时间才能见效，工党需要赢得另一场选举才能获得回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/reeves-resurrects-big-state-in-labour-s-bid-to-rebuild-britain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 20:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国扩大对阿斯利康的调查，中国首席执行官接受调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/astrazeneca-s-china-president-under-investigation-by-authorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着北京方面对这家英国制药巨头的监管审查不断加强并延伸至高层，阿斯利康公司中国区总裁王利民正在接受中国当局的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/astrazeneca-s-china-president-under-investigation-by-authorities</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:24:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
